This is a simple CRUD based project(CREATE RETIEVE UPDATE and DELETE) done in Eclipse  using JAVA and Mysql Database. 
The INSERT, SELECT, UPDATE and DELETE statements can be used in any database system, because this is support by all relational database systems.

Features of Project:
The system shall be able to record Book details : name,edition,price. 
The system  shall be able to retrieve the Book details : name,edition,price.
Then system shall be able to Edit and Delete the Book details : name,edition,price.
